WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.731 --> 00:00:06.169
That would mean he's not
the only agent in Japan.

2
00:00:08.206 --> 00:00:12.040
If I kill him. I'll be suspected.

3
00:00:13.311 --> 00:00:19.614
But what if all the FBI agents
on this case were to die?

4
00:00:21.003 --> 00:00:23.836
Hey. Light.

5
00:00:23.872 --> 00:00:26.773
The FBI aren't criminals.

6
00:00:30.012 --> 00:00:32.446
Killing them anyway?

7
00:00:36.118 --> 00:00:38.985
"Minami-Aoyama Catholic Church"

8
00:00:45.494 --> 00:00:46.586
Raye.

9
00:00:46.628 --> 00:00:49.188
I'm sorry. Naomi.

10
00:00:49.231 --> 00:00:52.359
I just got a call.
I'll join you later.

11
00:00:52.401 --> 00:00:55.063
But Father made time for us.

12
00:00:55.103 --> 00:00:56.502
Patch things up for me.

13
00:00:58.000 --> 00:01:04.074
Watch Online Movies and Series for FREE
www.osdb.link/lm

14
00:02:32.367 --> 00:02:39.000
"Raye Iwamatsu. I am Kira.
Use the transceiver inside."

15
00:02:39.041 --> 00:02:42.841
"I will talk to you directly."

16
00:02:59.928 --> 00:03:02.658
Hello. I am Kira.

17
00:03:03.665 --> 00:03:06.190
I am watching your every move.

18
00:03:06.969 --> 00:03:09.699
Do not look around. Face forward.

19
00:03:11.306 --> 00:03:14.742
Remember. I can always kill you.

20
00:03:18.947 --> 00:03:21.780
How will I know you're not a fake?

21
00:03:22.517 --> 00:03:25.247
I'll show you.
See the man sitting next to you

22
00:03:25.287 --> 00:03:30.418
His name is Taruhito Ozaki.
arrested for rape two years ago.

23
00:03:30.459 --> 00:03:39.094
But the victims feared revenge.
and did not press charges against him.

24
00:03:39.134 --> 00:03:44.663
He deserves to be punished.

25
00:03:45.574 --> 00:03:49.340
Taruhito Ozaki heart attack

26
00:03:49.378 --> 00:03:52.176
Taruhito Ozaki sits on
the right hand side of the train.

27
00:03:52.214 --> 00:03:54.978
After it leaves Akasakabashi Station.

28
00:03:55.017 --> 00:03:59.977
he will die quietly from a heart attack.

29
00:04:02.424 --> 00:04:04.153
Stay calm.

30
00:04:04.893 --> 00:04:11.696
Now quietly. see if he's dead and
make him look like he's sleeping.

31
00:04:34.823 --> 00:04:38.190
Do you believe I'm Kira now?
You killed him just to prove that?

32
00:04:39.194 --> 00:04:42.721
Just answer my questions.

33
00:04:42.764 --> 00:04:50.830
Tell me how many people from the FBI
are here in Japan.

34
00:04:53.475 --> 00:04:58.913
If you refuse. I'll start killing
the passengers one by one.

35
00:05:08.090 --> 00:05:13.187
There are 11 people besides myself.

36
00:05:15.764 --> 00:05:19.291
Do you know
all their names and faces?

37
00:05:20.802 --> 00:05:22.360
No.

38
00:05:24.172 --> 00:05:27.767
I'm telling you the truth.

39
00:05:28.276 --> 00:05:35.148
But surely. you must know
who your leader is. don't you?

40
00:05:36.618 --> 00:05:38.313
I do.

41
00:05:38.820 --> 00:05:42.381
You'll find five pieces of paper.

42
00:05:50.165 --> 00:05:55.933
Write down the name of your leader
inside the blank of the first page.

43
00:05:55.971 --> 00:05:58.132
Accurately.

44
00:05:58.173 --> 00:06:02.109
If you make it up.
I'll know immediately.

45
00:06:02.144 --> 00:06:04.635
I wouldn't dare if I were you.

46
00:06:26.568 --> 00:06:29.036
Cut on the computer.

47
00:06:29.070 --> 00:06:34.007
You'll soon get all 12 IDs of
the FBI from your leader.

48
00:06:34.476 --> 00:06:36.103
"Free Access Available"

49
00:07:07.709 --> 00:07:09.404
I've got it.

50
00:07:10.779 --> 00:07:12.371
Open it.

51
00:07:20.288 --> 00:07:25.624
Look at the pictures of the agents
attached to their IDs...

52
00:07:25.660 --> 00:07:31.064
and fill in their names accurately
inside the rest of the blanks.

53
00:08:21.650 --> 00:08:23.015
Done.

54
00:08:23.852 --> 00:08:29.051
Now. put them back in the envelope.
and place it on the rack.

55
00:08:56.184 --> 00:09:00.382
Get off at Shinagawa Park Station.

56
00:09:01.056 --> 00:09:03.991
And leave the transceiver behind.

57
00:09:37.792 --> 00:09:39.282
Raye.

58
00:09:42.831 --> 00:09:44.321
Naomi?

59
00:09:51.139 --> 00:10:10.481
Raye!

60
00:10:12.927 --> 00:10:14.986
Raye...

61
00:10:15.964 --> 00:10:17.989
Raye!

62
00:11:30.238 --> 00:11:33.605
Raye Iwamatsu. heart attack.

63
00:11:36.110 --> 00:11:42.310
Cancels all schedule. and
rides the train from Akasakabashi.

64
00:11:42.350 --> 00:11:46.013
Gets on the 10:14 train

65
00:11:46.054 --> 00:11:48.682
from the last door of the fourth car.

66
00:11:49.557 --> 00:11:52.287
He takes the manila envelope...

67
00:11:54.496 --> 00:11:58.091
and dies three seconds after
getting off.

68
00:12:06.441 --> 00:12:08.341
Five in Tokyo. three in Kanagawa.

69
00:12:08.376 --> 00:12:10.401
and four others.

70
00:12:10.445 --> 00:12:13.209
They all died of heart attacks.

71
00:12:13.248 --> 00:12:19.710
Their leader in Washington is said
to have died at the same hour.

72
00:12:20.121 --> 00:12:22.112
FBI agents?

73
00:12:22.156 --> 00:12:29.585
They were instructed by L
to secretly investigate the case.

74
00:12:29.631 --> 00:12:33.465
By L? Did you know about this?

75
00:12:33.501 --> 00:12:36.732
It's all out of the blue.

76
00:12:39.974 --> 00:12:42.738
"A Report on FBI Activities"

77
00:12:43.344 --> 00:12:48.338
The FBI agents that were
investigating the case died.

78
00:12:49.784 --> 00:12:52.514
All heart attacks.

79
00:12:53.788 --> 00:12:59.226
Kira is now killing people
besides criminals.

80
00:13:02.330 --> 00:13:07.199
It is possible that
we may all become targets.

81
00:13:07.969 --> 00:13:09.129
You should think carefully...

82
00:13:09.170 --> 00:13:16.269
about your families
and your loved ones.

83
00:13:18.112 --> 00:13:22.344
You are free to drop out of
this investigation.

84
00:13:23.585 --> 00:13:28.818
I guarantee that you will not
be demoted or punished for doing so.

85
00:13:29.524 --> 00:13:35.759
Those of you who are not afraid to
risk everything can stay.

86
00:13:38.466 --> 00:13:45.235
Lastly. I thank those
who fought with us till this day.

87
00:14:35.289 --> 00:14:38.019
There's only six of us.

88
00:14:38.059 --> 00:14:41.324
Watari and I are with you.

89
00:14:41.362 --> 00:14:45.992
I have faith in people who have
a strong sense of justice.

90
00:14:46.034 --> 00:14:48.195
L.

91
00:14:48.236 --> 00:14:52.866
I'm sorry but
it's getting hard to trust you.

92
00:14:52.907 --> 00:14:58.743
You give us orders from a safe place.
keeping yourself hidden at all times.

93
00:14:58.780 --> 00:15:01.374
How can you expect us to trust you?

94
00:15:01.416 --> 00:15:04.385
We can't have you working with us.

95
00:15:04.419 --> 00:15:06.444
He's right.

96
00:15:06.487 --> 00:15:11.322
To tell the truth.
I've also had doubts about you.

97
00:15:12.126 --> 00:15:16.495
You tend to take drastic measures.

98
00:15:19.667 --> 00:15:27.130
However. your cooperation is
essential to finding Kira.

99
00:15:27.175 --> 00:15:34.104
If you want to work with us.
why don't you show yourself?

100
00:15:36.384 --> 00:15:40.411
And then we could fight together.

101
00:15:41.189 --> 00:15:42.349
Fine.

102
00:15:42.390 --> 00:15:43.652
Watari.

103
00:15:50.598 --> 00:15:54.591
I will take you to L.

104
00:17:02.505 --> 00:17:05.099
How do you do. I'm L.

105
00:17:16.252 --> 00:17:18.846
I am Yagami.

106
00:17:18.888 --> 00:17:19.513
Ukita.

107
00:17:19.555 --> 00:17:20.180
Aizawa.

108
00:17:20.222 --> 00:17:20.779
Mogi.

109
00:17:20.823 --> 00:17:21.517
Sanami.

110
00:17:21.557 --> 00:17:22.251
Matsuda.

111
00:17:26.328 --> 00:17:27.989
Hey you!

112
00:17:28.030 --> 00:17:33.263
If I were Kira. you'd be dead by now.

113
00:17:33.302 --> 00:17:35.099
What do you mean?

114
00:17:35.137 --> 00:17:37.230
From what we know so far...

115
00:17:37.273 --> 00:17:39.537
Kira needs the names and features

116
00:17:39.575 --> 00:17:41.736
of the targets in order to kill them.

117
00:17:41.777 --> 00:17:46.180
From now on. do not
give out your real names.

118
00:17:46.215 --> 00:17:50.618
As for myself. call me Ryuzaki.

119
00:17:52.221 --> 00:17:53.483
Alright.

120
00:17:56.992 --> 00:18:02.225
Kira can also manipulate
one's behavior before death.

121
00:18:03.566 --> 00:18:10.199
The suicide notes written in jail
were probably Kira's experiment.

122
00:18:10.239 --> 00:18:11.536
Experiment?

123
00:18:11.574 --> 00:18:13.599
He tested them to see how accurately

124
00:18:13.642 --> 00:18:17.635
he could kill the FBI agents.

125
00:18:17.680 --> 00:18:21.514
He's sent a message to me
through their suicide notes.

126
00:18:21.550 --> 00:18:23.814
Did Kira do that. too?

127
00:18:23.852 --> 00:18:28.346
The agents died eight days after
this experiment.

128
00:18:28.390 --> 00:18:31.723
During that time. he somehow got

129
00:18:31.760 --> 00:18:35.423
the names from one particular agent.

130
00:18:35.864 --> 00:18:39.095
Kira is someone
within the authority...

131
00:18:39.134 --> 00:18:42.570
marked by the FBI.
before the experiment.

132
00:18:42.605 --> 00:18:44.402
Exactly.

133
00:18:44.440 --> 00:18:47.841
That should be easy to narrow down.

134
00:18:47.876 --> 00:18:48.968
Sure.

135
00:18:50.412 --> 00:18:57.614
Gathering from Kira's behavior.
he is very immature and hates to lose.

136
00:18:58.954 --> 00:19:00.854
Just like me.

137
00:19:01.457 --> 00:19:05.450
I've been losing up till now
but things are going to change.

138
00:19:05.494 --> 00:19:10.989
Let's win this together.

139
00:19:11.033 --> 00:19:12.830
Ryuzaki.

140
00:19:12.868 --> 00:19:18.465
This isn't a game.
this is an investigation.

141
00:19:18.507 --> 00:19:21.772
Our purpose is no different.

142
00:19:30.419 --> 00:19:34.947
"Busjacker Killed in Accident"

143
00:19:55.577 --> 00:20:00.105
"11 a.m. Kyonan Bus"

144
00:20:07.589 --> 00:20:11.320
"Investigation Closed"

145
00:20:22.137 --> 00:20:24.867
I've collected all the tapes.

146
00:20:27.676 --> 00:20:31.203
The ones from the security camera.

147
00:20:31.246 --> 00:20:32.736
Thanks for the trouble.

148
00:21:08.584 --> 00:21:10.017
This is him.

149
00:21:12.788 --> 00:21:14.653
Oh yes. he was sitting at the back.

150
00:21:14.690 --> 00:21:15.987
I remember.

151
00:21:16.024 --> 00:21:19.152
He was quarreling with a young man
when the robber came on the bus.

152
00:21:19.194 --> 00:21:21.560
What did this young man look like?

153
00:21:21.597 --> 00:21:27.661
Handsome.
Not that I have a thing for boys.

154
00:21:27.703 --> 00:21:33.608
Brave too. He didn't seem afraid
when the gun was pointed at him.

155
00:21:33.642 --> 00:21:36.304
Was he questioned by the police?

156
00:21:36.345 --> 00:21:40.338
No. Actually. he disappeared.

157
00:21:41.917 --> 00:21:44.784
Maybe he didn't want to be involved. either.

158
00:21:46.288 --> 00:21:48.017
Here.

159
00:21:49.725 --> 00:21:51.784
And this...

160
00:22:59.595 --> 00:23:02.792
You've narrowed down the list?

161
00:23:02.831 --> 00:23:04.458
Yes.

162
00:23:04.499 --> 00:23:06.091
Who's on it?

163
00:23:20.515 --> 00:23:23.245
The Chief's and Deputy Chief's families.

164
00:23:24.019 --> 00:23:27.216
Why don't you explain?

165
00:23:28.924 --> 00:23:34.226
This is the moment of
Agent Iwamatsu's death.

166
00:23:34.263 --> 00:23:38.393
As you can see.
he is pointing towards the train.

167
00:23:39.234 --> 00:23:40.997
Someone was on it?

168
00:23:41.036 --> 00:23:43.129
Presumably Kira.

169
00:23:51.179 --> 00:23:52.840
Who is she?

170
00:23:52.881 --> 00:23:55.008
Iwamatsu's fianc�.

171
00:23:56.351 --> 00:24:02.483
She was a talented FBI agent
who used to work under me.

172
00:24:03.158 --> 00:24:09.927
She probably noticed something unusual
and decided to follow him.

173
00:24:09.965 --> 00:24:12.957
Let's contact her right away.

174
00:24:13.001 --> 00:24:16.562
She's disappeared since his death.

175
00:24:16.605 --> 00:24:20.769
He must have been onto somebody.

176
00:24:20.809 --> 00:24:23.744
And we are one of them.

177
00:24:23.779 --> 00:24:27.977
With a probability of
less than three percent.

178
00:24:28.016 --> 00:24:29.449
Questioning us?

179
00:24:29.484 --> 00:24:30.974
No.

180
00:24:31.019 --> 00:24:38.016
We'll set up cameras and bugs
in both your houses.

181
00:24:38.060 --> 00:24:41.894
We cannot allow
this kind of outrage!

182
00:24:41.930 --> 00:24:44.228
If this comes out. we're all fired.

183
00:24:44.266 --> 00:24:47.724
I thought we weren't afraid
to risk everything.

184
00:24:51.873 --> 00:24:54.808
Fine. Let's do it.

185
00:24:54.843 --> 00:24:56.037
Chief!

186
00:24:56.078 --> 00:24:59.775
Check for any blind spots.
and do it thoroughly.

187
00:24:59.815 --> 00:25:02.375
What about your wife and daughter?

188
00:25:02.417 --> 00:25:07.116
I'm aware!

189
00:25:07.155 --> 00:25:09.851
But we'll never clear ourselves
if we avoid this.

190
00:25:09.891 --> 00:25:16.592
We'll set the cameras and bugs for.
shall we say. seven days.

191
00:25:16.631 --> 00:25:22.001
Why don't we have Chief
watch his own family then?

192
00:25:22.037 --> 00:25:23.834
Alright.

193
00:25:25.440 --> 00:25:29.103
Mr. Yagami and I will watch his house.

194
00:25:29.144 --> 00:25:33.012
Rest of you take turns
and watch Mr. Kitamura's.

195
00:25:56.872 --> 00:25:59.033
This man...

196
00:25:59.074 --> 00:26:00.871
Recognize him?

197
00:26:02.377 --> 00:26:04.811
He was following Light.

198
00:26:05.881 --> 00:26:07.815
Something the matter?

199
00:26:10.452 --> 00:26:12.079
He died.

200
00:26:15.123 --> 00:26:20.186
He was killed by Kira
while investigating the case.

201
00:26:25.467 --> 00:26:29.062
Hey. Light.

202
00:26:29.104 --> 00:26:31.072
Why are you scheduling deaths
for weeks ahead?

203
00:26:31.106 --> 00:26:38.274
So as not to be suspected. in case
I'm hospitalized or tied up somehow.

204
00:26:39.047 --> 00:26:41.106
You think of everything.

205
00:26:41.850 --> 00:26:44.614
Welcome to my show...

206
00:26:44.653 --> 00:26:48.054
"Misamisa's Happy Sweets"

207
00:26:48.090 --> 00:26:52.356
Here's what I'm making today.

208
00:26:53.095 --> 00:26:54.722
Can't wait!

209
00:26:54.763 --> 00:26:58.221
Fatten your friends with
croissant-pudding!

210
00:27:03.171 --> 00:27:04.763
What is it?

211
00:27:05.707 --> 00:27:07.334
Nothing.

212
00:27:12.147 --> 00:27:16.948
You can fatten your rival in love
as much as five kilos.

213
00:27:17.652 --> 00:27:22.021
My rival would be?
the pop star. Ai Otsuka.

214
00:27:22.457 --> 00:27:28.089
But I ended up getting fat instead!

215
00:27:28.130 --> 00:27:30.189
Now who's the devil?

216
00:27:31.633 --> 00:27:34.830
Croissant-pudding completed.

217
00:27:34.870 --> 00:27:38.306
Let's make pigs out of our rivals in love!

218
00:27:38.340 --> 00:27:39.739
Excellent!

219
00:27:40.509 --> 00:27:43.569
Who do you respect the most?

220
00:27:45.614 --> 00:27:47.514
Kira.

221
00:27:47.549 --> 00:27:49.983
A follower of Kira. too?

222
00:27:50.018 --> 00:27:54.318
He's so cool being
the executioner and all.

223
00:27:54.356 --> 00:27:57.382
The youngsters should agree.

224
00:27:58.226 --> 00:28:03.095
Actually. Kira saved me.

225
00:28:03.131 --> 00:28:04.325
What do you mean?

226
00:28:04.366 --> 00:28:08.132
Misa. I've told you
not to talk about Kira.

227
00:28:08.170 --> 00:28:10.229
Why can't I?

228
00:28:10.272 --> 00:28:13.867
Please cut the bit about Kira.

229
00:28:14.743 --> 00:28:17.211
Where's my freedom?

230
00:28:18.980 --> 00:28:21.847
I can't ask about her private life?

231
00:28:21.883 --> 00:28:25.478
You can. but not on this subject.

232
00:28:25.520 --> 00:28:28.956
Everyone's talking about Kira.

233
00:28:30.058 --> 00:28:32.788
Thank you all!

234
00:28:32.827 --> 00:28:35.318
Bye!

235
00:28:54.516 --> 00:28:55.949
Light.

236
00:29:06.461 --> 00:29:09.760
This is Ms. Maki.

237
00:29:09.798 --> 00:29:13.097
She wants to ask you something.

238
00:29:15.237 --> 00:29:16.761
How do you do?

239
00:29:16.805 --> 00:29:17.931
Hello.

240
00:29:19.007 --> 00:29:21.840
I'm doing an article on Kira's case.

241
00:29:21.876 --> 00:29:26.040
I've heard you met Raye Iwamatsu.

242
00:29:27.349 --> 00:29:31.615
Remember the man on the bus
from the FBI?

243
00:29:32.621 --> 00:29:34.145
Oh him.

244
00:29:34.189 --> 00:29:39.183
He was killed by Kira
while investigating the case.

245
00:29:39.227 --> 00:29:41.354
I didn't know.

246
00:29:41.396 --> 00:29:42.488
You didn't?

247
00:29:42.530 --> 00:29:47.194
He was the one following Light.

248
00:29:48.236 --> 00:29:50.227
That's right.

249
00:29:50.272 --> 00:29:53.537
Because he suspected you were Kira.

250
00:29:53.575 --> 00:29:58.478
Are you trying to say I killed him?

251
00:29:58.513 --> 00:30:01.311
Kira can kill with a name.

252
00:30:01.349 --> 00:30:05.877
You've used the busjack to
find out Raye's name.

253
00:30:06.888 --> 00:30:09.516
That's funny.

254
00:30:09.557 --> 00:30:12.424
Did Raye die immediately afterwards?

255
00:30:12.460 --> 00:30:14.189
Three days later.

256
00:30:14.229 --> 00:30:21.658
If I were Kira. I would've killed him
as soon as I discovered his name.

257
00:30:21.703 --> 00:30:26.037
Light can't be Kira.

258
00:30:26.074 --> 00:30:28.201
You're wrong.

259
00:30:28.243 --> 00:30:30.438
And rude.

260
00:30:30.478 --> 00:30:32.639
I may sue you
so I'm putting down your words.

261
00:30:34.516 --> 00:30:37.508
Other agents died. too.

262
00:30:37.552 --> 00:30:42.990
But if you killed Raye first.
you thought you would be suspected.

263
00:30:43.024 --> 00:30:46.084
That's why he wasn't killed
right away.

264
00:30:46.127 --> 00:30:48.027
Am I wrong?

265
00:30:48.063 --> 00:30:50.623
All the agents died?

266
00:30:50.665 --> 00:30:52.997
I never heard that on the news.

267
00:30:53.034 --> 00:30:54.968
It was kept a secret.

268
00:30:57.138 --> 00:30:59.868
You're making it up.

269
00:31:00.275 --> 00:31:03.676
I didn't know she was such a person.

270
00:31:03.712 --> 00:31:05.805
On the subway...

271
00:31:05.847 --> 00:31:10.045
you somehow found out the names

272
00:31:10.085 --> 00:31:11.916
of the agents and killed them all.

273
00:31:17.592 --> 00:31:20.755
This is a waste of time. Let's go.

274
00:31:24.966 --> 00:31:26.900
Light Yagami.

275
00:31:27.836 --> 00:31:33.706
You can't kill me.
I've given you my false name.

276
00:31:35.977 --> 00:31:38.138
Go away.

277
00:31:39.180 --> 00:31:41.648
Raye was my fianc�.

278
00:31:42.917 --> 00:31:48.787
I'll hunt Kira down and won't stop
till I put him behind bars.

279
00:31:51.426 --> 00:31:53.519
What was that?

280
00:31:53.561 --> 00:31:55.529
She's crazy.

281
00:31:56.831 --> 00:31:58.731
False name. huh?

282
00:32:07.108 --> 00:32:11.272
Another one's on your tail.

283
00:32:13.214 --> 00:32:16.581
Sure you don't want my eyes?

284
00:32:19.053 --> 00:32:22.113
You're in deep shit.

285
00:33:05.900 --> 00:33:13.773
The people who set-up the cameras told me
that Light checked for signs of entry.

286
00:33:16.110 --> 00:33:21.047
Other than that. we found
nothing suspicious in his room.

287
00:33:21.082 --> 00:33:24.574
Were all those cameras necessary?

288
00:33:24.619 --> 00:33:30.785
Light's characteristics.
his IQ and lifestyle...

289
00:33:30.825 --> 00:33:33.851
they all fit the profile.

290
00:33:33.895 --> 00:33:37.058
This is a waste of time.

291
00:33:37.732 --> 00:33:42.931
If there's even a speck of doubt.
we must continue.

292
00:33:42.971 --> 00:33:46.998
Without that determination.
we'll never catch Kira.

293
00:33:54.115 --> 00:33:59.018
Hey Light. talk to me.
No one's watching.

294
00:34:01.556 --> 00:34:03.683
Give me an apple.

295
00:34:03.725 --> 00:34:06.717
I demand one!

296
00:34:09.230 --> 00:34:11.790
Come on!

297
00:34:20.708 --> 00:34:22.198
Apples?

298
00:34:29.050 --> 00:34:30.813
What's wrong?

299
00:34:32.754 --> 00:34:36.952
L's onto me completely.

300
00:34:36.991 --> 00:34:39.687
Someone's been in my room.
I smell it.

301
00:34:39.727 --> 00:34:45.290
There are cameras and bugs
hidden everywhere.

302
00:34:49.737 --> 00:34:54.470
L wasn't so easy to deal with after all.

303
00:34:54.509 --> 00:34:58.878
As long as I'm being watched.
there are no apples for you.

304
00:34:59.280 --> 00:35:01.373
What?!

305
00:35:02.116 --> 00:35:06.450
Let's look for the cameras
and find a blind spot.

306
00:35:39.387 --> 00:35:45.417
Your son is a hard worker.
You must be very proud.

307
00:35:48.129 --> 00:35:51.326
He wishes to join the Police Agency.

308
00:35:53.301 --> 00:35:57.260
How will my son be cleared?

309
00:35:57.305 --> 00:36:00.570
If he does nothing suspicious.

310
00:36:00.608 --> 00:36:03.941
and there's a murder by Kira.

311
00:36:04.812 --> 00:36:08.248
You want us to wait for a murder?

312
00:36:08.282 --> 00:36:10.307
It seems so.

313
00:36:14.422 --> 00:36:16.117
Have one.

314
00:36:25.833 --> 00:36:28.768
DAY THREE

315
00:36:31.172 --> 00:36:34.232
It's dinnertime!

316
00:36:46.921 --> 00:36:48.752
I'm taking a break.

317
00:37:01.235 --> 00:37:05.137
Chief. you must rest.

318
00:37:05.173 --> 00:37:08.199
You haven't slept in three days.

319
00:37:09.243 --> 00:37:14.112
How could I.
when my family are being suspected.

320
00:37:23.891 --> 00:37:26.018
Yes? Understood.

321
00:37:32.400 --> 00:37:37.030
We have confirmed the deaths of...

322
00:37:37.071 --> 00:37:42.031
three killers that were on the run.
and two convicts on death row.

323
00:37:42.076 --> 00:37:44.101
Is that so?

324
00:37:45.346 --> 00:37:47.314
Not too fast.

325
00:37:48.916 --> 00:37:53.319
Have you forgotten
that Kira can manipulate time?

326
00:37:54.989 --> 00:38:01.224
We won't know for sure
until a new crime is reported.

327
00:38:15.443 --> 00:38:19.812
DAY FIVE

328
00:39:01.222 --> 00:39:02.849
DAY SEVEN

329
00:39:02.890 --> 00:39:05.358
Aren't you worried?

330
00:39:05.393 --> 00:39:07.861
Dad hasn't come home in a week.

331
00:39:07.895 --> 00:39:09.692
I'm used to it.

332
00:39:10.598 --> 00:39:13.567
Father's hard at work.
You should be. too.

333
00:39:13.601 --> 00:39:15.091
Okay.

334
00:39:17.338 --> 00:39:21.365
Eating chips after dinner
You're gonna get fat.

335
00:39:21.409 --> 00:39:25.846
I'll be up all night studying.
I need my strength.

336
00:39:25.880 --> 00:39:27.108
Thanks for dinner.

337
00:39:30.618 --> 00:39:31.949
Wow!

338
00:39:58.880 --> 00:40:05.012
Trading ended
with a recovery of 10.800 dollars.

339
00:40:05.052 --> 00:40:08.681
This morning. crude oil price
had declined to...

340
00:40:08.723 --> 00:40:13.387
60 dollars per barrel.

341
00:40:17.031 --> 00:40:21.627
We have just received
new information.

342
00:40:21.669 --> 00:40:26.299
The suspect accused of kidnapping
a five-year-old girl in Edogawa...

343
00:40:26.340 --> 00:40:29.070
has been arrested.

344
00:40:29.110 --> 00:40:36.607
Toru Kashimayama. age 29.
allegedly kidnapped Kasumi Miuchizawa.

345
00:40:36.651 --> 00:40:41.554
Her body was found buried
under the floor of his apartment.

346
00:40:41.589 --> 00:40:46.652
On the 28th of last month. Kasumi was
playing in a park near her home...

347
00:40:46.694 --> 00:40:56.365
where she was last seen
climbing into a red car.

348
00:40:56.404 --> 00:40:59.271
He's not watching the news.

349
00:41:28.269 --> 00:41:32.706
Something seems to have happened
at the scene.

350
00:41:32.740 --> 00:41:34.264
Mr. Murai

351
00:41:34.308 --> 00:41:36.538
Live from Funabori.

352
00:41:36.577 --> 00:41:41.207
Kashimayama has just died.

353
00:41:41.248 --> 00:41:43.944
According to information...

354
00:41:43.985 --> 00:41:49.048
Kashimayama was said to have been
in the middle of an interrogation...

355
00:41:49.090 --> 00:41:53.186
when he suddenly died of
heart attack.

356
00:41:53.227 --> 00:41:55.695
Mr. Murai?

357
00:41:55.730 --> 00:41:59.222
Do you suspect Kira?

358
00:41:59.767 --> 00:42:05.603
The cause of death is still unknown.
but there is that possibility.

359
00:42:05.639 --> 00:42:07.869
This is Kira's latest crime.

360
00:42:07.908 --> 00:42:10.706
Light is no longer under suspicion.

361
00:42:11.645 --> 00:42:14.808
Isn't that enough?

362
00:42:16.183 --> 00:42:18.014
Ryuzaki!

363
00:42:49.116 --> 00:42:53.416
"TORU KASHIMAYAMA"

364
00:42:53.687 --> 00:42:57.282
The Chief's and Deputy Chief's families
are cleared.

365
00:42:58.859 --> 00:43:03.228
Ryuzaki. aren't you satisfied?

366
00:43:05.299 --> 00:43:07.199
Watari.

367
00:43:07.234 --> 00:43:11.762
Recover all the bugs and cameras
from their houses.

368
00:43:11.806 --> 00:43:13.637
Understood.

369
00:43:14.842 --> 00:43:17.242
You must be relieved. Chief.

370
00:43:17.278 --> 00:43:19.542
It'll be a fresh start.

371
00:43:37.731 --> 00:43:41.792
Light. the cameras are all gone.

372
00:44:03.657 --> 00:44:07.093
There's nothing like
eating apples...

373
00:44:07.128 --> 00:44:09.187
free from the public eye.

374
00:44:13.033 --> 00:44:15.866
But Light.

375
00:44:15.903 --> 00:44:20.806
What if your sister had taken
that bag of chips?

376
00:44:22.476 --> 00:44:26.606
I'm the only one
who likes consomm� flavor.

377
00:44:55.976 --> 00:45:00.276
A phone call from Naomi Misora.

378
00:45:03.751 --> 00:45:05.378
It's been a while.

379
00:45:06.086 --> 00:45:07.644
L.

380
00:45:08.789 --> 00:45:14.523
As of now. I will prove to you
that Light Yagami is Kira...

381
00:45:15.496 --> 00:45:17.589
by risking my life.

382
00:45:28.375 --> 00:45:32.038
"Shiori"

383
00:45:33.214 --> 00:45:34.943
Hello?

384
00:45:34.982 --> 00:45:37.382
Can we meet?

385
00:45:37.418 --> 00:45:38.510
Where?

386
00:45:38.552 --> 00:45:39.814
The art gallery.

387
00:45:39.853 --> 00:45:42.822
I was just thinking about you.

388
00:45:44.191 --> 00:45:46.250
When can you come?

389
00:45:47.328 --> 00:45:51.662
I can leave right now so...
in 30 minutes.

390
00:45:52.733 --> 00:45:54.462
Light...

391
00:45:55.536 --> 00:45:57.527
You sound strange.

392
00:46:03.611 --> 00:46:05.203
Shiori?

393
00:46:18.025 --> 00:46:21.961
We're monitoring the art gallery.

394
00:46:21.996 --> 00:46:23.896
Let me see it.

395
00:46:36.610 --> 00:46:38.271
I'm at the entrance.

396
00:46:38.312 --> 00:46:40.177
Come inside.

397
00:46:40.214 --> 00:46:44.617
I'll be by Ekusuhso Kenak's
"Mask and Death".

398
00:46:44.652 --> 00:46:46.142
Alright.

399
00:46:50.557 --> 00:46:53.321
We can see how Kira kills?

400
00:46:53.360 --> 00:46:56.295
What do you mean by that?

401
00:47:05.639 --> 00:47:07.266
Light?

402
00:47:08.542 --> 00:47:11.705
I knew it. Kira is Light.

403
00:47:14.815 --> 00:47:18.148
Is my son still a suspect?

404
00:47:31.298 --> 00:47:32.492
Shiori.

405
00:47:32.533 --> 00:47:34.000
Light!

406
00:47:34.668 --> 00:47:36.693
Forgive me.

407
00:47:36.737 --> 00:47:38.432
Light Yagami.

408
00:47:39.606 --> 00:47:44.805
If you want to see her alive.
confess right now.

409
00:47:46.347 --> 00:47:48.315
That you've killed Raye.

410
00:47:49.383 --> 00:47:51.749
And that you are Kira!

411
00:47:55.556 --> 00:47:57.023
Get some cops in there!

412
00:48:00.928 --> 00:48:03.294
You've got it all wrong.

413
00:48:03.330 --> 00:48:04.797
I'm not Kira.

414
00:48:04.832 --> 00:48:07.300
If you keep on lying...

415
00:48:09.002 --> 00:48:10.264
I'll kill her.

416
00:48:10.304 --> 00:48:11.828
No!

417
00:48:12.406 --> 00:48:15.807
Even if I were.
she has nothing to do with it.

418
00:48:15.843 --> 00:48:18.243
Kill me instead!

419
00:48:18.278 --> 00:48:23.113
I'll teach you the pain of
losing your loved one.

420
00:48:23.150 --> 00:48:24.777
Don't do it!

421
00:48:25.686 --> 00:48:27.745
Please. not Shiori.

422
00:48:27.788 --> 00:48:29.187
Light...

423
00:48:30.524 --> 00:48:32.719
How miserable you are!

424
00:48:33.761 --> 00:48:39.927
The almighty Kira.
begging for his girlfriend's life.

425
00:48:39.967 --> 00:48:43.266
I'm telling you. I'm not Kira!

426
00:48:43.303 --> 00:48:45.066
You can't kill without a name.

427
00:48:45.105 --> 00:48:46.834
I'll tell you mine.

428
00:48:50.644 --> 00:48:53.272
Naomi Misora.

429
00:48:54.515 --> 00:49:04.413
Naomi is in katakana characters.
and Misora. Chinese ones.

430
00:49:05.459 --> 00:49:12.456
Now that you know my name.
go ahead and kill me!

431
00:49:19.339 --> 00:49:21.432
Naomi Misora...

432
00:49:24.578 --> 00:49:25.306
The police?

433
00:49:25.345 --> 00:49:26.835
They're almost there.

434
00:49:26.880 --> 00:49:29.815
No. hold them back a little longer.

435
00:49:29.850 --> 00:49:31.181
What?

436
00:49:31.218 --> 00:49:32.913
Here's the good part.

437
00:49:32.953 --> 00:49:36.980
How dare you! This isn't a show.

438
00:49:37.724 --> 00:49:40.420
You want to save her?

439
00:49:40.461 --> 00:49:42.656
Then kill me.

440
00:49:43.497 --> 00:49:46.057
Like you did Raye.

441
00:49:46.099 --> 00:49:49.660
Like all the criminals
you've executed.

442
00:49:49.703 --> 00:49:54.572
Go on and kill
without laying a hand on me!

443
00:49:54.608 --> 00:49:57.406
But I'm not Kira!

444
00:50:51.498 --> 00:50:52.590
Shiori!

445
00:50:53.534 --> 00:50:56.002
Please... no.

446
00:50:56.703 --> 00:50:58.534
Shiori...

447
00:50:59.873 --> 00:51:02.967
This can't be happening!

448
00:51:03.944 --> 00:51:04.740
Shiori?

449
00:51:15.489 --> 00:51:16.979
She's armed.

450
00:51:17.357 --> 00:51:21.191
Shiori. hang in there.

451
00:51:21.228 --> 00:51:23.492
Shiori.

452
00:51:23.530 --> 00:51:25.122
Light...

453
00:51:25.799 --> 00:51:27.164
Shiori...

454
00:51:37.911 --> 00:51:42.473
That was... our last kiss.

455
00:51:57.931 --> 00:51:59.865
Why?!

456
00:52:01.101 --> 00:52:03.399
Why did you shoot her?

457
00:52:04.304 --> 00:52:08.297
Tell me!

458
00:52:17.851 --> 00:52:19.182
Stop!

459
00:52:29.696 --> 00:52:33.826
This was a miscalculation.

460
00:52:34.368 --> 00:52:41.331
Naomi Misora's miscalculation was
that I saw her.

461
00:52:41.375 --> 00:52:47.211
She also shouldn't have told me
she was Raye's fianc�.

462
00:52:47.948 --> 00:52:50.940
Nobody uses false names on weddings.

463
00:52:51.752 --> 00:52:54.812
The church is open to everyone.

464
00:52:55.422 --> 00:52:59.688
so it was easy to find out her name.

465
00:53:06.366 --> 00:53:09.494
Naomi Misora. suicide.

466
00:53:10.237 --> 00:53:16.005
Arranges to meet with
her fianc�'s killer.

467
00:53:16.043 --> 00:53:22.642
Takes his girlfriend hostage
at the Omei Art Gallery.

468
00:53:22.683 --> 00:53:28.781
She makes the girlfriend call him
on April 15th. 14:15.

469
00:53:30.190 --> 00:53:36.254
She then contacts a third party;
the Investigation Team...

470
00:53:36.296 --> 00:53:42.326
and tries to make the killer confess
as they watch.

471
00:53:43.070 --> 00:53:49.634
At 14:55. she stops
the hostage from running away...

472
00:53:51.712 --> 00:53:57.947
but in a moment of madness.
ends up shooting herself.

473
00:54:19.139 --> 00:54:20.731
I'm sorry.

474
00:54:22.609 --> 00:54:25.976
If only we'd gotten here earlier.

475
00:54:31.618 --> 00:54:33.950
I'll send for a car.

476
00:54:40.761 --> 00:54:45.391
Didn't expect Shiori to die.
did you?

477
00:54:53.907 --> 00:54:59.174
I'm the one who killed Shiori.

478
00:54:59.212 --> 00:55:00.702
Huh?

479
00:55:01.448 --> 00:55:04.781
With the help of "Death Note".

480
00:55:04.818 --> 00:55:07.480
But how?

481
00:55:08.021 --> 00:55:13.653
Naomi ended up killing Shiori.
but you can't make people kill.

482
00:55:14.461 --> 00:55:19.831
If you write their names.
they'd all die of heart attacks.

483
00:55:20.267 --> 00:55:22.758
I know.

484
00:55:24.070 --> 00:55:30.908
That's why I wrote Shiori's name
on the page next to Naomi's.

485
00:55:40.520 --> 00:55:45.389
Shiori Akino.
killed by a third person.

486
00:55:46.927 --> 00:55:51.193
Get's kidnapped
at the Omei Art Gallery.

487
00:55:51.231 --> 00:55:59.161
On April 15th. 14:15. she is
forced to call up her boyfriend.

488
00:56:00.207 --> 00:56:04.576
She gets away
as the police break in.

489
00:56:04.611 --> 00:56:06.203
But at 14:55.
a warning shot hits her...

490
00:56:06.246 --> 00:56:14.483
and she dies trying to protect
her boyfriend.

491
00:56:17.357 --> 00:56:20.724
It didn't have to say anything about
Naomi shooting Shiori or vice versa.

492
00:56:21.294 --> 00:56:24.786
It didn't have to say anything about
Naomi shooting Shiori or vice versa.

493
00:56:24.831 --> 00:56:30.030
Does that mean.
Naomi just happened to kill Shiori?

494
00:56:30.070 --> 00:56:32.538
A coincidence?

495
00:56:33.707 --> 00:56:39.703
That's hardly a perfect scheme
for killing Shiori.

496
00:56:40.413 --> 00:56:44.713
It was no coincidence.
I planned everything.

497
00:56:46.386 --> 00:56:52.916
All I wrote was that
Shiori would be killed by a gunshot.

498
00:56:52.959 --> 00:56:58.659
And that Naomi would carry a gun
in order to shoot herself.

499
00:56:58.698 --> 00:57:03.101
No one carries a gun around
in Japan...

500
00:57:03.136 --> 00:57:09.268
which means that the gun Naomi has.
would be shot at Shiori.

501
00:57:11.745 --> 00:57:13.975
Hear this.

502
00:57:14.014 --> 00:57:19.919
"Death Note" changes our destinies
in the most natural way.

503
00:57:20.887 --> 00:57:24.414
So even though it wasn't written.

504
00:57:25.125 --> 00:57:28.094
everything went according to my plan.

505
00:57:28.128 --> 00:57:32.360
You're a devil in disguise.

506
00:57:37.537 --> 00:57:41.769
My girlfriend was killed
before my eyes.

507
00:57:41.808 --> 00:57:47.371
If I tell them I want to
join the team and capture Kira...

508
00:57:47.414 --> 00:57:53.114
everyone would sympathize and
believe me without a doubt.

509
00:58:04.130 --> 00:58:06.064
Light. you know what?

510
00:58:06.099 --> 00:58:13.005
You're far worse than god of death.

511
00:58:15.775 --> 00:58:19.973
Shiori truly loved you.

512
00:58:21.581 --> 00:58:26.280
Didn't you love her at all?

513
00:58:30.857 --> 00:58:33.417
I don't know.

514
00:58:42.469 --> 00:58:45.961
Misa. I know you're lonely.

515
00:58:46.006 --> 00:58:48.406
Don't come close to me!

516
00:58:48.441 --> 00:58:52.309
You're the one who said
you wanted to die.

517
00:58:52.345 --> 00:58:54.609
I didn't say such a thing.

518
00:58:54.647 --> 00:58:58.048
Let's go to heaven.
Your parents are waiting.

519
00:58:58.084 --> 00:58:59.949
We'll go together.

520
00:59:03.289 --> 00:59:06.281
You're an assistant director.

521
00:59:07.127 --> 00:59:11.223
I'll tell. and you'll lose
your job forever!

522
00:59:11.698 --> 00:59:17.000
I've been watching you
at the studio. in the hallway.

523
00:59:17.637 --> 00:59:21.073
We'll die together.
I'm giving you my life.

524
00:59:22.108 --> 00:59:24.099
That's my destiny.

525
00:59:24.144 --> 00:59:25.577
Moron!

526
00:59:26.413 --> 00:59:31.476
Who said I want to go to heaven
or to hell?

527
00:59:38.425 --> 00:59:42.259
Don't worry. It won't hurt a bit.

528
00:59:42.996 --> 00:59:44.964
No...

529
00:59:46.566 --> 00:59:50.366
